publisher			Interplay Inc.							
publish_time	 2000年11月1日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Sacrifice is the acclaimed real-time strategy game that focuses on combat instead of resource gathering. The only two resources you'll need to worry about are mana and souls. Need more units? Capture the souls of your enemy. Cast spells of awesome power. Choose which gods to support and you will be rewarded with a different selection of spells. 					Banish your enemy by sacrificing one of your allies at his altar...						
